          "prompt_html": "<h1>NOTE COMPLETION 56</h1><p><strong>Questions 31 - 40</strong></p><p>Complete the notes below.</p><p>Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</p><p>The Bosco Verticale in Milan, two innovative buildings in Milan</p><p><strong>Bosco Verticale: an overview</strong></p><p>‘Bosco Verticale’ = vertical forest</p><p>The two blocks of flats are 30 minutes by foot from Milan’s <blank data-qid=\"q31\"/></p><p><strong>Facts and figures</strong></p><p>The two buildings are</p><ul><li>110 metres tall with 26 floors</li><li>76 metres tall with 18 floors</li></ul><p>The balconies have been planted with:</p><ul><li>900 trees</li><li><blank data-qid=\"q32\"/> 20,000</li></ul><p><strong>Advantages of the design</strong></p><p>The greenery:</p><ul><li>gives the buildings an <blank data-qid=\"q33\"/></li><li>appearance</li><li>removes bits of <blank data-qid=\"q34\"/></li><li>from the air (pollution is bad in Milan)</li><li>controls humidity</li><li>provides <blank data-qid=\"q35\"/></li><li>at warmer times of the year</li><li>reduces noise</li></ul><p><strong>Design and construction</strong></p><p>Boeri Studio (architects) worked with botanists to choose the right trees and plants</p><p>Various species were positioned according to the amount of <blank data-qid=\"q36\"/> they require</p><p>The biodiversity of the ‘living walls’ should draw birds as well as <blank data-qid=\"q37\"/> to the area</p><p><blank data-qid=\"q38\"/> were used to move the plants into position</p><p><strong>Maintenance</strong></p><p>The plants are watered using grey water (from sinks &amp; showers); this is a sustainable solution</p><p>The vegetation belongs to management, who look after it (not the residents)</p><p>To reach the plants for maintenance, gardeners can either:</p><ul><li>go through the flats and onto the balconies, or</li><li>come down using <blank data-qid=\"q39\"/> connected to a structure on the roof, if access is difficult</li></ul><p><strong>Responses to the building</strong></p><p>The building was well received and won prizes, but also received some <blank data-qid=\"q40\"/></p>",
